{"tid":896482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陝西地下水重金屬超標　羊群暴斃","createTime":"2018-11-10T05:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T06:36:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2110f3820a4a3b1ea5c28fa0ebc5c93e08616421","tid":896482,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:28:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181110/20542647\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181110%2F20542647&d=gKsu5e2IlVg3nxeHSNKNb0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=f4e391c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181110%2F20542647&h=dc6cc26e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181110/20542647</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月10日 <br />\n<br />\n陝西地下水重金屬超標　羊群暴斃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181110/large/a1504a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181110%2Flarge%2Fa1504a.gif&h=a3755f05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受污染的地下水。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地水質受污染導致生態災難的豈止福建泉州！媒體披露，陝西省小壕兔鄉因煤礦開採和天然氣勘探活動影響，水質受污染，當地井水變混濁黃水、農地無法耕種、牲畜離奇暴斃。北京獨立藝術家堅果兄弟今年7月辦展，將該地污水當展品，引起當局關注；環境部門跟進調查發現，當地水中含鐵、錳等重金屬含量，超過國家標準4.2倍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「得病即死　沒法救」<br />\n<br />\n小壕兔鄉位於陝西榆林市，居民平均年收入約1萬元人民幣（約1.1萬港元），多年來居民一直抱怨當地水污染，指農場和飲用的地下水受2005年啟動的中石化天然氣項目污染，民眾苦不堪言，玉米地種不成新苗，羊離奇發高燒，一群一群地死，連人也得了怪病。其中，村民王成家100多隻羊去年死了20多隻，今年又死了20多隻，死狀幾乎一模一樣：發高燒，肚瀉，尿結石；王成說：「得病不到五個小時就死，獸醫看了看，說跟人得癌症一樣，沒法救。」<br />\n<br />\n北京獨立藝術家堅果兄弟為當地居民抱不平，今年7月在北京一畫廊搞實物展，展出9,000瓶水，將從小壕兔鄉採集的混濁地下水水樽擺在展場內。事件引有關部門關注。陝西當地環境局隨後展開調查，發現11個水樣本有10個不合格，不合格項目為鐵、錳等指標，當局隨後要求區內中石化華北油氣分公司採氣一廠停止生產，另外還有三家煤礦也被叫停生產。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n記者戴口罩稱「空氣達標」 　遭當場質問<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n明鏡網︰習女兒返哈佛讀博士　改姓瞿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n魚排老闆口麻痹入ICU　轟當局隱瞞<br />\n記者戴口罩稱「空氣達標」 　遭當場質問<br />\n毒油污腐蝕眼珠福建現「生化魚屍」校方逼上課　多名小童不適"},{"pid":"472289dce55197194746877218ea706d2f4aee37","tid":896482,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n羊肉大減價"},{"pid":"14e676f7b2665eff5da925358e45b5a27ad8ddca","tid":896482,"uid":70786,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"472289dce55197194746877218ea706d2f4aee37","tid":896482,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n羊肉大減價"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:38:30.000Z","msg":"繼平牛肉平豬肉後又有一批平羊肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57d9036ecfed696a80c1d10aea43ad51995cd78","tid":896482,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:49:11.000Z","msg":"而家D 00後咁唔捱得"},{"pid":"6806d48caae5307b6d1d5534a610b2d0c9f10371","tid":896482,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:49:36.000Z","msg":"支那境內 好正常啫"},{"pid":"a832da13abf7108d53a30a1e58dac2544f8c12b6","tid":896482,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"472289dce55197194746877218ea706d2f4aee37","tid":896482,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br